{"manifest_version":1,"info":{"id":"zain_backup","name":"Zain's Backup","author":"iamzainnnn","version":"V35.2-hotfix","changelog":"V35.2 — Hotfix\n\n🛠 Fixed\n\n- Fixed an issue where video effects and filters were not being applied properly in Stories.\n- Fixed a blank screen issue that could occur after uploading a Story.\n- Fixed incorrect corner rounding on Reels shared to Stories.\n- Fixed follow status synchronization issues.\n- Applied additional memory leak, media rendering, and stability fixes for improved reliability.\n\n🔄 Improved\n\n- Improved Story sticker responsiveness and motion prediction.\n- Improved search suggestions and typeahead responsiveness.\n- Refined Homecoming behavior after navigating through Reels.\n- Improved audio processing for smoother playback and media handling.\n- Improved Story profile bubble interactions with a larger tap area.\n- Enhanced Story reshare compatibility with Spotify content."},"backup":{"50769:":["23: : false"],"53982:":["0: : true"],"64040:":["0: : false","3: : false","2: : false","1: : false"],"69718:":["4: : true"],"102290:":["1: : true","2: : true","0: : true"],"77485:":["4: : true"],"122807:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"102713:":["0: : true"],"121581:":["3: : true","2: : true","1: : true","0: : true"],"70831:":["15: : true","13: : true","11: : false","10: : true","12: : true"],"55842:":["0: : true"],"101311:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"109190:":["0: : true"],"108768:":["2: : true","0: : true"],"60946:":["0: : false"],"101226:":["3: : true"],"101332:":["14: : true","0: : true","6: : true","4: : true","2: : true","10: : true","9: : false"],"124097:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"103620:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"96703:":["0: : true"],"106882:":["0: : false"],"103969:":["0: : true"],"105615:":["8: : true","7: : true","3: : false","1: : true","2: : true","6: : false","5: : true","9: : true","4: : true"],"123680:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"83747:":["0: : true"],"106908:":["0: : true"],"89057:":["0: : true"],"121677